{"tid":1611626,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"(同我推) 幾點關於現場抗爭極重要既提醒","createTime":"2019-10-02T04:13:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T08:25:45.000Z","uid":147696,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"435194e509116210fcd708db77745f8c17def46d","tid":1611626,"uid":147696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T04:13:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1:對準政權</span></span><br />\n<br />\n政府機構，包括政府入股既公司機構<br />\n中聯辦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中共政黨例如工聯會禮義廉<br />\n<br />\n至於其他親中機構，抵制罷買罷食就得，正如對得把口既愛國人士我地都唔洗出神獸一樣道理，不過咁，如果人地一郁手，唔該我地要狠狠咁還擊!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">2: 全民full gear</span></span><br />\n<br />\n求下你地唔好再吊帶拖鞋涼鞋出黎，1個口罩就企前線。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />講過好多次啦，點解仲係要咁，豬咀眼罩頭盔冰袖加背囊係基本野，冇人知道幾時你身處既位置變左做前線。睇戲既寧願你返屋企睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，要be water又唔夠快，搞到手足因為你俾人捉又唔好，你被捉又唔好。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">3: 前線勇武</span></span><br />\n<br />\n唔打就等狗差唔多set好陣全撤，打既就未set好陣，狗未夠就同佢打。琴日多區開花，其實警力唔係想像中咁多，沙田區都分左一班係第一城，反觀源和路200警都唔知有冇。200好多? 我地人仲多啦，唔好話勇武，3000人沖過去，俾你都淆啦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外，勇武係要傾，要陣式，要士氣，呢方面要諗諗計。同埋，唔該at least 用盾用Gip la,遮點推進呀，人地用實彈啦而家。香港人唔係好有錢嫁咩?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">4: 前線守備</span></span><br />\n<br />\n冇錯呀，唔好再用3角鐵防啦， 10分鍾扎，人地一跳就過，一剪就破。3角鐵係用黎攻嫁，尖位對出去推。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點防?火魔法，油，鐵釘等都好，但當你諗住近攻時，其實重防等於收緊左自己退路。反之黑警既進攻係有距離，佢地唔會1次過同你走200米，因為咁好易令陣型分散，容易落單。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">5: 和理非裝備</span></span><br />\n<br />\n除左以上既gear裝野，你地可以帶好多野，<br />\n1. 鎖 (公園閘，黨鐵閘，咩都好)<br />\n2. 雀巢咖啡加長襪 (自己諗點解)<br />\n3. 一支700ml水 (tg, prevention of dehydration)<br />\n4. 毛巾 (fracture做 pad 又得，俾魔法師又得，咁當然汗都要抹下嘅 <br />\n5. 替換衫<br />\n6. Gatsby 濕紙巾( 藍色水)<br />\n7. 長遮<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">6.  諗個岩你既崗位做</span></span><br />\n<br />\n出得去就係要做野，臨時物資站又好，哨兵又好，FA, 滅煙，前線，鼓隊，魔法師，唔該唔好行行企企得唔得。想提返大家，係得現場，就可以非法集結，琴日，就可以係告你暴動，你地有覺悟未? 未既，去第2區或同區安全地方以街坊look幫手等散場時接仔女，一定有你既崗位。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">7 有關散場指引</span></span><br />\n<br />\n走唔該至少急步，而家係走難咁走，攰唔係籍口，返去操返好自己體能先。除左走果陣1 2 1 2 ，唔該唔好背脊對住敵人，大忌黎嫁，同埋，要救手足!我建議係，去到組隊，8人一組，要走一齊走，被捉一齊救。組與組間互相呼應，當然要做好都要時間，希望下次更加好。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">8.  唔好俾仇恨蓋過理智，令我地做左我地唔想做既人。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n黑警仆街都唔夠政權仆街。我地對抗黑警係因為佢係政權最後一個堡壘，攻唔到我地冇可能令呢個政權回應訴求。我地目標唔係打死佢，係令佢地退，走，散，只要有1區做到，破窗效應就到佢地受返。<br />\n<br />\n對自己友都係,be humble, 用rationale 唔好emotion去講野okay?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後，<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">各自努力</span></strong>唔係形容現場抗爭，而係唔同抗爭方法上利用自己專長去各自努力。<br />\n<br />\n去到現場，我地就係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>同一</strong></span>， 唔要各自，要一齊呀!<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港，時代革命</span></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"46bce2336959143177ec6405da4d96c87e216e92","tid":1611626,"uid":147696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T04:30:46.000Z","msg":"光復香港，時代革命"},{"pid":"a82728cbfde52c721484da9d187186728de3a1dc","tid":1611626,"uid":147696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T04:31:09.000Z","msg":"光復香港，時代革命"},{"pid":"421031901c2fea1cfaf5c57b372c31ef827fb1a0","tid":1611626,"uid":147696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T04:31:24.000Z","msg":"光復香港，時代革命"},{"pid":"7246900fd5afb0f6d12e71fe00422a01909c779a","tid":1611626,"uid":147696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T04:31:37.000Z","msg":"光復香港，時代革命"},{"pid":"86bc42c349303cced0cbd92cdc9cf86b4f9cc0ba","tid":1611626,"uid":147696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T04:40:55.000Z","msg":"光復香港，時代革命"},{"pid":"cc461d85f1c27d7e08f0e3b68d9b518d39b4ec51","tid":1611626,"uid":147696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T04:41:06.000Z","msg":"光復香港，時代革命"},{"pid":"02661fc94aaa5b7377adce70c964a1ff28343140","tid":1611626,"uid":147696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T04:42:08.000Z","msg":"光復香港，時代革命"},{"pid":"268abe7c028cf484965bd730f8fc5727e7d8f2be","tid":1611626,"uid":147696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T04:42:35.000Z","msg":"光復香港，時代革命"},{"pid":"20a27f2284e15d73b9ccae0aa18550f95e003b3d","tid":1611626,"uid":147696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T04:55:20.000Z","msg":"光復香港，時代革命"},{"pid":"e9f4a0a980a8a2250949f8c99e5166e01caf54fe","tid":1611626,"uid":297630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T05:06:12.000Z","msg":"推呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58a8b2b1c7dd252d19347873371f6dbc24c3dcba","tid":1611626,"uid":297630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T06:50:38.000Z","msg":"Agger <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d28ea3424f8bc54272f1b7d44e07d2c31eb95440","tid":1611626,"uid":147696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T08:25:45.000Z","msg":"從推<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">對準政權呀！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我唔同意琴日又破壞中銀，360同Starbucks 等中資機構，罷食罷買超合作就得，除非成班沖出黎郁手就話。<br />\n<br />\n不割，可改善"}]}